parameters:
\SE\SE[15]Oh my, everyone! \SE[15]Do you need any items or
something!? (It's not free though!)

\SM[nod]\SE[2]Phew... It took longer than I thought. Let's go to
Laura and the others...
スライドスピード = def

I'm struggling in life! Love will surely save the world!! Please,
take the first step and extend a helping hand too! ... It seems
like I'm receiving money from people passing by.

It looks like a crystal for teleportation. It says Still under
preparation.

The crystal for teleportation is shining... Will you go to the
transfer space?

It seems like the cat's business tools. Various things seem to be
packed inside...

Ulyssean Swordsmanship ~ Beginners Welcome ~ Dojo Invaders also
Welcome!

I am guarding the castle gate. Please leave if you have no
business here.

The torch next to me is so hot... I feel like I'm turning into a
steamed octopus inside this armor...

Are you here for official business within the castle? I'm sorry,
but please leave.
Orolo...!! Ugh... I drank too much... Orolo...!!

The water here is purified, so it's clean. You can drink it if
you want, but it's better to avoid it.

I am on duty! It is mandatory to have security guards stationed
at the weapons trading post!

Today is a wonderful day... The flowers are blooming. The birds
are chirping...

If you'd like! How about staying overnight?! My mom's cooking is
delicious, you know!

I... drank too much alcohol... Let me rest for a little... just a
little...

Having stairs on the walking course really makes a difference.
It's like the quality of the day improves...

I made this goddess statue 10 years ago... but now I'm concerned
about the sculpting. Could you let me shave off just a little bit
of the cheeks...?

Ugh... I drank too much... Ahh... This is bad. I'm going to die.
Me.

How about worshiping the gods of Ulyssean? If you're willing, how
about making an offering as well?
地下道クリア後に出現…。

This path continues to the underground passage... Will you jump
in?
Seriously...? You found this place...? You're a little scary...
